name: Red Wall
description: Red Wall is a infinite digital loop. The base image in this work is a photo-collage that was taken on the rooftop of a retail building in West LA. The black square was added as a reference to Kazimir Malevich. This animation serves as an extension of the core ideas at the heart of my photographic practice, i.e., creating urban dreamscapes that defy time and space, and the re-contextualizing of the physical world.
